(22033, 'Loratan 10mg m.r. 10 tab', 'لوراتان 10مجم ام ار 10 قرص', '', '17', 'Loratadine', 'T3a pharma', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'مضاد للحساسية', 'Antihistamine.antiallergy', '10mg', 'Loratadine is a 2nd generation antihistamine and is used to manage symptoms of allergic rhinitis, wheal formation, urticaria, and other allergic dermatologic conditions.[A176435][A176438][L8486]', '6223005980229', '', 2743, '2022-12-06', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
